```py
select *
from dim_contracts
where
  valid_from <= '2023-01-01 01:00:00'
  and (valid_to > '2023-01-01 01:00:00'
       or valid_to is null)
```

```py
select *
from dim_contracts
where
  valid_from <= '2023-01-01 00:00:01'
  and (valid_to >= '2023-01-01 00:00:01'
       or valid_to is null)
```

```py
select *
from dim_contracts
where
  '2023-01-01 00:00:01' between
  valid_from and valid_to
```
